hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Another year evergreen pharmacy elmhurst hours Local grocer Cathy Torcasio, 38, had no plan to leave. The resident of the fire-ravaged Springwood suburb of Faulconbridge was at work on Wednesday when the emergency was declared. Her husband and son were at home filling gutters and bins with water and preparing for the worst. “It all depends on the wind. You’ve just got to wait and see,” she said. “I have a fire plan. If I see a fire, run.”
